# unite-mdfind

gather candidates by mdfind (mac only).

## unite source

    :Unite mdfind

    :Unite mdfind:<onlyin_directory_path>

## unite action

* :Unite file
* &lt;Tab&gt;
* you can select mdfind action

## you can define map to action

    inoremap <silent><buffer><expr> <C-s> unite#do_action('mdfind')

## Inspired by

* unite-everything
